{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_StalkerAttack}}
'''A_StalkerAttack'''

(no parameters)

If the calling actor has the {{flag|NOGRAVITY}} flags, it is put in its Drop state. Otherwise, and if it has a valid target, calls [[A_FaceTarget]]. If in addition said target is within melee range, it is inflicted 2d8 melee damage.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Stalker}} and derived classes.

